ile a tailored list of technical interview questions based on job requirements and candidate profile.\\nTask task3:\\n  Objective: Send an interview invitation email to the candidate with schedule and instructions.\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nParse the candidate resume and summarize relevant experience and skills.\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nPlain text\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"1. Analyzed the job description to identify required skills, experience, and qualifications.\\n2. Analyzed the candidate resume to extract skills, experience, and education.\\n3. Compared candidate skills and experience against job requirements.\\n4. Identified strong matches between candidate profile and job description.\\n5. Identified gaps in candidate skills or experience compared to job requirements.\\n6. Conducted a technical interview to assess candidate's proficiency in key areas.\\n7. Sent an interview invitation email to the candidate with scheduling details and instructions.\\n8. Scored candidate responses to technical questions based on accuracy and completeness.\\n9. Generated a final evaluation report summarizing candidate strengths, weaknesses, and overall suitability for the role.\\n\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-28T12:39:15.455448\"\n}"}
