andidate responses: (To be completed in Task task5)\\n6. Generate final evaluation report: (To be completed after scoring)\\n```\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nTask task6:\\n  Objective: Generate the final evaluation report combining job requirements, resume summary, and scored responses, and compile a .txt file documenting all steps taken throughout the process.\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nScore the candidate's interview responses against defined criteria.\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nJSON\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"Interview Evaluation\\\": {\\n    \\\"Candidate\\\": \\\"[Candidate Name]\\\",\\n    \\\"Role\\\": \\\"[Job Title]\\\",\\n    \\\"Date\\\": \\\"[Date]\\\",\\n    \\\"Scoring\\\": {\\n      \\\"Question 1\\\": {\\n        \\\"Question\\\": \\\"Describe a complex microservices architecture you designed.\\\",\\n        \\\"Candidate Response Summary\\\": \\\"[Summarize Candidate's Response]\\\",\\n        \\\"Score\\\": \\\"[Score out of 10]\\\",\\n        \\\"Rationale\\\": \\\"[Explain the scoring]\\\",\\n        \\\"Red Flags\\\": \\\"[Note any red flags or inconsistencies]\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"Question 2\\\": {\\n        \\\"Question\\\": \\\"How does AWS ECS compare to Kubernetes (EKS)? When would you choose one over the other?\\\",\\n        \\\"Candidate Response Summary\\\": \\\"[Summarize Candidate's Response]\\\",\\n        \\\"Score\\\": \\\"[Score out of 10]\\\",\\n        \\\"Rationale\\\": \\\"[Explain the scoring]\\\",\\n        \\\"Red Flags\\\": \\\"[Note any red flags or inconsistencies]\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"Question 3\\\": {\\n        \\\"Question\\\": \\\"You need to optimize a slow API endpoint. Outline your step-by-step approach.\\\",\\n        \\\"Candidate Response Summary\\\": \\\"[Summarize Candidate's Response]\\\",\\n        \\\"Score\\\": \\\"[Score out of 10]\\\",\\n        \\\"Rationale\\\": \\\"[Explain the scoring]\\\",\\n        \\\"Red Flags\\\": \\\"[Note any red flags or inconsistencies]\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"Question 4\\\": {\\n        \\\"Question\\\": \\\"Compare PostgreSQL, MongoDB, and Redis for a high-throughput system. Provide use cases and trade-offs.\\\",\\n        \\\"Candidate Response Summary\\\": \\\"[Summarize Candidate's Response]\\\",\\n        \\\"Score\\\": \\\"[Score out of 10]\\\",\\n        \\\"Rationale\\\": \\\"[Explain the scoring]\\\",\\n        \\\"Red Flags\\\": \\\"[Note any red flags or inconsistencies]\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"Question 5\\\": {\\n        \\\"Question\\\": \\\"How do you approach writing unit tests and practicing TDD?\\\",\\n        \\\"Candidate Response Summary\\\": \\\"[Summarize Candidate's Response]\\\",\\n        \\\"Score\\\": \\\"[Score out of 10]\\\",\\n        \\\"Rationale\\\": \\\"[Explain the scoring]\\\",\\n        \\\"Red Flags\\\": \\\"[Note any red flags or inconsistencies]\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"Question 6\\\": {\\n        \\\"Question\\\": \\\"Describe a complex production issue you debugged. What observability tools and processes did you use?\\\",\\n        \\\"Candidate Response Summary\\\": \\\"[Summarize Candidate's Response]\\\",\\n        \\\"Score\\\": \\\"[Score out of 10]\\\",\\n        \\\"Rationale\\\": \\\"[Explain the scoring]\\\",\\n        \\\"Red Flags\\\": \\\"[Note any red flags or inconsistencies]\\\"\\n      },\\n      \\\"Question 7\\\": {\\n        \\\"Question\\\": \\\"Explain RESTful API design best practices, including versioning and documentation.\\\",\\n        \\\"Candidate Response Summary\\\": \\\"[Summarize Candidate's Response]\\\",\\n        \\\"Score\\\": \\\"[Score out of 10]\\\",\\n        \\\"Rationale\\\": \\\"[Explain the scoring]\\\",\\n        \\\"Red Flags\\\": \\\"[Note any red flags or inconsistencies]\\\"\\n      },\\n       \\\"Follow-up Questions\\\": {\\n        \\\"Question\\\": \\\"[The follow-up question asked]\\\",\\n        \\\"Candidate Response Summary\\\": \\\"